# Week 4 — SCADA / HMI Implementation

## Overview

Week 4 focuses on building the **Supervisory Control and Data Acquisition (SCADA)** layer for the ICS-RedSim lab environment.
This phase involves deploying a Human Machine Interface (HMI) that allows operators to **monitor and control the industrial process in real time**.

The SCADA system was implemented using **FUXA**, an open-source web-based SCADA platform designed for industrial monitoring and visualization.

By connecting the SCADA system to the PLC using **Modbus TCP**, the operator interface can display process data and send control commands to the PLC.

---

# Objectives

The key objectives of Week 4 include:

* Deploy the SCADA platform
* Connect SCADA to the PLC using Modbus TCP
