# SCADA System Architecture

The SCADA system acts as a **supervisory layer** between operators and industrial controllers.

### SCADA Communication Flow

```
Operator Interface (HMI)
        |
        | Modbus TCP
        |
SCADA Server (FUXA)
        |
        |
PLC Controller (OpenPLC)
        |
        |
Industrial Process Simulation
```

This architecture allows operators to monitor system behavior and issue commands through a graphical interface.

